Halcyon Hires Wigan to Lead Fundraising Drive Abroad, FT Says

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-03-15T10:04:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/halcyon-hires-wigan-to-lead-fundraising-drive-abroad-ft-says.html
Halcyon Asset Management LLC, a
U.S. hedge-fund firm, is developing its business in the U.K. as
it seeks fresh sources of capital from institutions in  Europe ,
the Middle East and  Australia , the Financial Times reported.  The firm, which has $10 billion under management, has hired
Rollo Wigan to direct fundraising in  London  and plans to recruit
more research analysts, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in London on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 